(5)Department of Neuroscience and Behaviour, Division of Psychiatry, Ribeirão 
Preto Medical School, University of São Paulo, Ribeirão Preto, São Paulo, 
Brazil.
(6)Population Mental Health Center, University of São Paulo, São Paulo, Brazil.
(7)Department of Preventive Medicine, Faculty of Medicine, University of São 
