Synthesis, ADMET Prediction, and Antitumor Profile of Phenoxyhydrazine- 
1,3-thiazoles Derivatives.

de Siqueira LRP(1)(2), de Lima Ferreira LP(1)(2), de Oliveira Filho GB(1), de 
Oliveira MVG(1), Pinto AF(1), de Melo Silva VG(1), de Moraes Gomes PAT(1), de 
