Author information:
(1)Laboratory of Planning in Medicinal Chemistry, Department of Pharmaceutical 
Sciences, Center for Health Sciences, Federal University of Pernambuco, 
50740-520, Recife, PE, Brazil.
(2)Therapeutic Innovation Research Center, Federal University of Pernambuco, 
