(3)Laboratory of Prospection of Bioactive Molecules, University of Pernambuco, 
56328-903, Petrolina, PE, Brazil.
(4)Laboratory of Cell Biology, Institute Oswaldo Cruz, Fiocruz, Av. Brasil 4365, 
